<task id="task_xxj_4ml_jp">
    <title>Editing tags in the editor</title>
    <shortdesc>You can edit any of the tags that pre-exist in the template or that you have added to
        the document. This also allows you to add contextual information to the tags in your
        document .</shortdesc>
